      <title>贝莱德、先锋集团被指控违反反垄断法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/blackrock-vanguard-accused-of-antitrust-violations-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以德克萨斯州为首的几个州正在起诉贝莱德、先锋集团和道富银行，指控它们通过投资提高电价，违反了反垄断法。彭博社的 Sally Bakewell 参加了彭博公开利益讨论会，讨论了这起诉讼及其对 ESG 行业的影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/blackrock-vanguard-accused-of-antitrust-violations-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 15:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
