      <title>美联储青睐的通胀指标回升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/fed-s-preferred-measure-of-inflation-picks-up-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美国经济分析局的数据，核心个人消费支出价格指数（剔除波动性较大的食品和能源项目）较去年 10 月上涨 2.8%，较上月上涨 0.3%。Mike McKee 报道了“彭博未平仓合约”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/fed-s-preferred-measure-of-inflation-picks-up-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 15:13:13 GMT</pubDate>
